[arnaout020enriching] is an unsupervised pattern-based methodology that extracts salient negations from query logs. The intuition is that users often ask why something does not hold, as in ``Why didn't Stephen Hawking win the Nobel Prize in Physics?''. Such a query can then be used to deduce that Hawking did indeed not win the Nobel Prize.